Package: monitorgonio
Title: visualize Argos Goniometer output in the field
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-02-05
Authors@R: person("William R.", "Cioffi", email = "wrc14@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1182-8578"))
Author: William R. Cioffi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: William R. Cioffi <wrc14@duke.edu>
Description: A shiny app for visualizing the direction and strength of a ptt using a laptop connected to an Argos Goniometer. It just eavesdrops on the log file. Can be useful because the little handheld can be a pain to read on a bouncing boat.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
Imports:
	shiny,
	shinyFiles,
	plotrix
